Usage1: conf:update <pid> [name[=<value>]] ...

Update the specified configuration with the specified properties.
A property can be deleted by giving only name without '=<value>'.
A property can be set to empty by giving 'name=' with no value.

Usage2: conf:update <filter> [name[=<value>]] ...

Update all the configurations matching the specified filter with the specified
properties.
A property can be deleted by giving only name without '=<value>'.
A property can be set to empty by giving 'name=' with no value.
